Script logs into Gmail, composes an email, and sends it to scittest@auditram.com
using command-line inputs.
Install: pip install selenium webdriver-manager
Use personal Gmail, enable 2-Step Verification, create an App Password.
Run:
python email_automator.py --email "your@gmail.com" --password "APP_PASS" --subject "Test" --body "Message" --fresh-profile
Script opens Chrome, logs in, writes the mail, sends it, and saves screenshots.
